  /* === PDF EXPORT: HIDE DROPDOWNS SAFELY ===
     - Scope: only inside .pdf-stage overlay/wrapper
     - Triggers: hidden (keeps space) to avoid layout shifts
     - Menus/popovers: removed from flow so they don't appear in PDF
  */
  .pdf-stage :is(
    /* ARIA/generic */
    [aria-haspopup="menu"],
    [aria-haspopup="listbox"],
    [role="combobox"],
    /* Native */
    select,
    /* Common classes */
    .dropdown-toggle,
    .dropdown-trigger,
    .menu-trigger,
    /* Project-specific triggers */
    .btn-arrow,
    /* keep title visible; don't hide the wrapper */
  ){
    visibility: hidden !important;
    pointer-events: none !important;
  }

  .pdf-stage :is(
    /* ARIA roles */
    [role="menu"],
    [role="listbox"],
    /* Common classes */
    .dropdown-menu,
    .menu,
    .select-menu,
    /* Project-specific menus */
    .export-dropdown,
    .bucket-dropdown,
    /* Popper/tippy-like */
    [data-popper-placement]
  ){
    display: none !important;
  }

  /* Keep bucket title text visible, hide only the small arrow */
  .pdf-stage .bucket-title-wrapper .bucket-arrow{
    visibility: hidden !important;
    pointer-events: none !important;
  }

/* ====== UTILS ====== */
const toTitleCase = (s) => {
  if (!s || typeof s !== 'string') return s;
  return s.toLowerCase().split(' ').map(word => {
    if (word.length === 0) return '';
    return word.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + word.slice(1);
  }).join(' ');
};
const norm = (s) => String(s ?? "")
  .normalize("NFKC")
  .replace(/\u00A0/g," ")
  .replace(/\s+/g," ")
  .trim()
  .toLowerCase();
const normRosterName = (s) => String(s ?? "")
  .normalize("NFKD")
  .replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, "")
  .replace(/\u00A0/g," ")
  .replace(/\s+/g," ")
  .trim()
  .toLowerCase();

const parseItalianDate = (dateStr) => {
  if (!dateStr) return 0;
  const str = String(dateStr).trim();
  if (!str) return 0;

  const parseTime = (timeStr) => {
    const m = String(timeStr || '').match(/^(\d{1,2}):(\d{2})(?::(\d{2}))?$/);
    if (!m) return { hour: 0, minute: 0, second: 0 };
    return {
      hour: parseInt(m[1], 10) || 0,
      minute: parseInt(m[2], 10) || 0,
      second: parseInt(m[3], 10) || 0
    };
  };

  const parseDateToken = (token) => {
    if (!token) return null;
    let m = token.match(/^(\d{1,2})[\/\-.](\d{1,2})[\/\-.](\d{2,4})$/);
    if (!m) {
      m = token.match(/^(\d{1,2}):(\d{1,2}):(\d{2,4})$/); // formato gg:mm:aa
    }
    if (!m) return null;
    const day = parseInt(m[1], 10);
    const month = parseInt(m[2], 10);
    let year = parseInt(m[3], 10);
    if (!Number.isFinite(day) || !Number.isFinite(month) || !Number.isFinite(year)) return null;
    if (day < 1 || day > 31 || month < 1 || month > 12) return null;
    if (year < 100) year += 2000;
    return { day, month, year };
  };

  const parts = str.split(/\s+/);
  const dateToken = parts[0];
  const timeToken = parts[1] || '';
  const dateParts = parseDateToken(dateToken);
  if (dateParts) {
    const { day, month, year } = dateParts;
    const { hour, minute, second } = parseTime(timeToken);
    return new Date(year, month - 1, day, hour, minute, second).getTime();
  }

  if (/^\d{1,2}:\d{2}(:\d{2})?$/.test(dateToken)) {
    const { hour, minute, second } = parseTime(dateToken);
    const date = new Date();
    date.setHours(hour, minute, second, 0);
    return date.getTime();
  }

  return Date.parse(str) || 0;
};
const safeSvgId = (s) => String(s ?? "")
  .normalize("NFKD")
  .replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, "")
  .toLowerCase()
  .replace(/[^a-z0-9_-]+/g, "-")
  .replace(/^-+|-+$/g, "");
const fmt  = (n)=> new Intl.NumberFormat('it-IT').format(Math.round(n));
const toNum= (v)=>{
  const n = Number(String(v).replace(/\./g,'').replace(/\s/g,''));
  return Number.isFinite(n) ? n : 0;
};
const uniq = (list)=> Array.from(new Set(list)).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b, undefined, {numeric:true}));
const esc   = (s)=> String(s ?? '').replace(/[&<>"']/g, m => ({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;',"'":'&#39;'}[m]));
const escAttr=(s)=> esc(s).replace(/"/g,'&quot;');
const disp = (val)=> {
  if (val==null) return 'N/A';
  const n = typeof val === 'number' ? val : toNum(val);
  return Math.round(n) === 0 ? 'N/A' : fmt(n);
};

// Label ‚Äúcarine‚Äù: tutto minuscolo con iniziale maiuscola
// (IGS rimane sempre tutto maiuscolo)
function prettyLabel(s){
  if (!s) return '';
  return String(s)
    .split(' ')
    .map(w => {
      if (!w) return '';
      if (w.toUpperCase() === 'IGS') return 'IGS';
      const lower = w.toLowerCase();
      return lower.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + lower.slice(1);
    })
    .join(' ');
}

function capitalizeFirst(s){
  const str = String(s ?? '').trim();
  if (!str) return '';
  return str.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + str.slice(1);
}

function splitBrandCampaign(raw) {
  const s = String(raw ?? '').trim();
  if (!s) return { base: "", campaign: "" };
  const m = s.match(/^(.*?)\s*\(([^()]+)\)\s*$/);
  if (!m) return { base: s, campaign: "" };
  return { base: m[1].trim(), campaign: m[2].trim() };
}

function brandBase(raw) {
  return splitBrandCampaign(raw).base;
}

function brandCampaign(raw) {
  return splitBrandCampaign(raw).campaign;
}

function buildBrandLabel(base, campaign) {
  if (!base) return "";
  return campaign ? `${base} (${campaign})` : base;
}

function selectedBrandFullLabel() {
  if (!sel.brand) return "";
  if (sel.brand === "__ALL__") return "Tutte le attivit√†";
  const base = brandBase(sel.brand);
  return buildBrandLabel(base, sel.campaign);
}

function formatBrandForTable(raw) {
  const parts = splitBrandCampaign(raw);
  const baseLabel = prettyLabel(parts.base);
  if (!parts.campaign) return baseLabel;
  return `${baseLabel} (${capitalizeFirst(parts.campaign)})`;
}

function filterRowsBySelectedBrand(rows) {
  if (!sel.brand || sel.brand === "__ALL__") return rows;
  const baseNorm = norm(brandBase(sel.brand));
  return rows.filter(r => {
    const parts = splitBrandCampaign(r[COLS.brand]);
    if (norm(parts.base) !== baseNorm) return false;
    if (sel.campaign) return norm(parts.campaign) === norm(sel.campaign);
    return true;
  });
}

function getBrandBases(rows) {
  return uniq(rows.map(r => brandBase(r[COLS.brand])));
}

function getBrandCampaigns(rows, base) {
  if (!base) return [];
  const baseNorm = norm(brandBase(base));
  return uniq(rows.map(r => {
    const parts = splitBrandCampaign(r[COLS.brand]);
    if (norm(parts.base) !== baseNorm) return "";
    return parts.campaign;
  }).filter(Boolean));
}

function getTalentBrandSourceRows() {
  if (!sel.talent || !sel.year) return [];
  const byT = DATA.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent]) === norm(sel.talent));
  const byY = byT.filter(r => norm(String(r[COLS.year])) === norm(String(sel.year)));
  if (!sel.month || sel.month === "__ALL_MONTHS__") return byY;
  return byY.filter(r => monthKey(r[COLS.month]) === monthKey(sel.month));
}

function talentBrandHasCampaigns(base) {
  const baseName = brandBase(base);
  if (!baseName || baseName === "__ALL__") return false;
  return getBrandCampaigns(getTalentBrandSourceRows(), baseName).length > 0;
}

function brandModeHasCampaigns(base) {
  const baseName = brandBase(base);
  if (!baseName) return false;
  return getBrandCampaigns(DATA, baseName).length > 0;
}

function getBrandModeStepMap() {
  const needsCampaign = !!sel.brand && brandModeHasCampaigns(sel.brand);
  if (needsCampaign) {
    return { brand: 0, campaign: 1, talent: 2, year: 3, month: 4, needsCampaign: true };
  }
  return { brand: 0, campaign: null, talent: 1, year: 2, month: 3, needsCampaign: false };
}

function isTalentSelectionComplete() {
  if (!sel.brand) return false;
  if (sel.brand === "__ALL__") return true;
  if (!talentBrandHasCampaigns(sel.brand)) return true;
  return !!sel.campaign;
}

function isBrandSelectionComplete() {
  if (!sel.brand || !sel.month) return false;
  if (!brandModeHasCampaigns(sel.brand)) return true;
  return !!sel.campaign;
}


/* --- Mesi --- */
const MONTH_ABBR = {
  "gennaio":"GEN",
  "febbraio":"FEB",
  "marzo":"MAR",
  "aprile":"APR",
  "maggio":"MAG",
  "giugno":"GIU",
  "luglio":"LUG",
  "agosto":"AGO",
  "settembre":"SET",
  "ottobre":"OTT",
  "novembre":"NOV",
  "dicembre":"DIC",
};

function monthName(s){
  const raw = String(s||'').trim();
  const name = raw.replace(/^\s*\d{1,2}\s*[-‚Äì]\s*/,'').trim();
  const lower = name.toLowerCase();
  if (MONTH_ABBR[lower]) return MONTH_ABBR[lower];
  return name ? name.toUpperCase() : raw.toUpperCase();
}
function monthKey(m) {
  const s = String(m||'').trim();
  const hit = s.match(/^(\d{1,2})/);
  return hit ? parseInt(hit[1],10) : 99;
}

function monthLabelFromNumber(num) {
  const idx = Number(num) - 1;
  if (idx >= 0 && idx < MONTHS_CANONICAL.length) {
    return monthName(MONTHS_CANONICAL[idx]);
  }
  return String(num || '').padStart(2, '0');
}

function monthStampFromRow(r) {
  const m = monthKey(r[COLS.month]);
  if (!Number.isFinite(m) || m < 1 || m > 12) return null;
  const yearVal = parseInt(String(r[COLS.year] ?? '').trim(), 10);
  if (!Number.isFinite(yearVal)) return m;
  return (yearVal * 12) + m;
}

function labelFromMonthStamp(stamp) {
  if (!Number.isFinite(stamp)) return '';
  const year = Math.floor((stamp - 1) / 12);
  const month = stamp - (year * 12);
  const label = monthLabelFromNumber(month);
  return year ? `${label} ${year}` : label;
}

/* Bucket tipi contenuto */
function getBucket(t) {
  const s = String(t || "").toUpperCase().trim();
  if (!s) return "ALTRO";
  if (/^(IGS|STOR(E|Y)|INSTAGRAM STORIES?)\b/.test(s)) return "IGS";
  if (/^TIK\s*TOK|^TT\b/.test(s)) return "TIKTOK";
  if (/^REELS?\b/.test(s)) return "REEL";
  if (/^(POST|IG\s*POST)\b/.test(s)) return "POST";
  const m = s.match(/^[A-Z√Ä-√ú]+/); return m ? m[0] : "ALTRO";
}

function igsSetNum(typeStr){
  const s = String(typeStr||'');
  const m = s.match(/IGS[^0-9]*?(\d+)\s*[¬∞¬∫]?\s*SET/i);
  return m ? parseInt(m[1],10) : null;
}

const METRICS_BY_BUCKET = {
  IGS: ["reach", "link", "tag", "like"],
  TIKTOK: ["reach", "like", "commenti", "save", "share"],
  REEL: ["reach", "like", "commenti", "save"],
  POST: ["reach", "like", "commenti", "save"],
  ALTRO: ["reach", "like", "commenti", "save", "share"]
};

const METRIC_LABELS = {
  reach: "Reach",
  link: "Click Link",
  tag: "Click Tag",
  like: "Mi Piace",
  commenti: "Commenti",
  save: "Salvataggi",
  share: "Condivisioni"
};

function isValidMetricValue(v) {
  if (v == null || v === '' || v === 'N/A') return false;
  const str = String(v).trim();
  if (str === '' || str === 'N/A' || str.toLowerCase() === 'n/a') return false;
  const n = Number(str.replace(/\./g, '').replace(/\s/g, ''));
  return Number.isFinite(n);
}

function sumMetric(arr, col) {
  return arr.reduce((a, r) => a + toNum(r[col]), 0);
}

function avgMetric(arr, col) {
  const validValues = arr.filter(r => isValidMetricValue(r[col]));
  return validValues.length ? sumMetric(validValues, col) / validValues.length : 0;
}

function updatePdfModeLabel() {
  if (!els.pdfModeLabel) return;
  const map = {
    media: "Media",
    somma: "Somma",
    both: "Media + Somma"
  };
  els.pdfModeLabel.textContent = map[exportAggMode] || "Media";
}



function setStateMessage(msg, type='neutral'){
  if (!els.state) return;
  if (!msg){
    els.state.innerHTML = "";
    els.state.style.display = 'none';
    return;
  }
  els.state.style.display = 'flex';
  const cls = type === 'error' ? 'bubble error' : 'bubble';
  els.state.innerHTML = `<span class="${cls}">${esc(msg)}</span>`;
}

if (els.btnRefresh) {
  els.btnRefresh.addEventListener('click', () => {
    window.location.reload();
  });
}


const loaderEl   = document.getElementById('loader');
const appFrameEl = document.querySelector('.app-frame');
let initialMenuOpen = false;

let DATA = [];
let searchMode = 'talent'; // 'talent' | 'brand' | 'roster' | 'estimate'

let step = 0; 
// In Talent mode: 0=Talent, 1=Year, 2=Month, 3=Brand, 4=Campaign (se presente)
// In Brand mode:  0=Brand, 1=Campaign (se presente), 2=Talent, 3=Year, 4=Month
let sel = { talent:"", year:"", month:"", brand:"", campaign:"" };
let aggMode = "media";
let exportAggMode = "media"; // modalit√† scelta nel popup per l'export

// e.g. { TIKTOK: 'ALL' | 'ADV' | 'NO_ADV', REEL: ... }
let bucketFilters = {}; 
let currentRosterDownloadLinks = ROSTER_DOWNLOAD_LINKS;


/* ====== MODE MENU LOGIC ====== */

function resetAllSelections() {
  sel = { talent:"", year:"", month:"", brand:"", campaign:"" };
  step = 0;
  editing = true;
  talentSearch = "";
  bucketFilters = {}; // Reset ADV filters
  setStateMessage("");
  renderAll();
}

/* Cambio modalit√† */
// Cambia da toggle a apertura menu
const modeMenuToggleBtn = document.getElementById('modeMenuToggle');
function updateModeToggleIcon() {
  if (!modeMenuToggleBtn) return;
  modeMenuToggleBtn.classList.remove("active", "roster", "estimate");
  if (searchMode === "brand") modeMenuToggleBtn.classList.add("active");
  if (searchMode === "roster") modeMenuToggleBtn.classList.add("roster");
  if (searchMode === "estimate") modeMenuToggleBtn.classList.add("estimate");
}
modeMenuToggleBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
  openModeMenu();
});

// Funzione per aprire il menu modale
function openModeMenu() {
  if (els.modeMenuModal && els.modeMenuModalOverlay) {
    els.modeMenuModalOverlay.classList.add('open');
    els.modeMenuModal.classList.add('open');
    if (initialMenuOpen && els.modeSections) {
      els.modeSections.forEach(section => section.classList.remove('active'));
    } else {
      updateActiveModeSection();
    }
  }
}

// Funzione per chiudere il menu modale
function closeModeMenu() {
  if (els.modeMenuModal && els.modeMenuModalOverlay) {
    els.modeMenuModalOverlay.classList.remove('open');
    els.modeMenuModal.classList.remove('open');
  }
  if (initialMenuOpen && appFrameEl) {
    appFrameEl.classList.remove('initial-menu');
    initialMenuOpen = false;
  }
}

// Aggiorna quale sezione √® marcata come attiva nel menu
function updateActiveModeSection() {
  if (els.modeSections) {
    els.modeSections.forEach(section => {
      const mode = section.getAttribute('data-mode');
      if (mode === searchMode) {
        section.classList.add('active');
      } else {
        section.classList.remove('active');
      }
    });
  }
}

// Event listener per le sezioni del menu
if (els.modeSections) {
  els.modeSections.forEach(section => {
    section.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const selectedMode = section.getAttribute('data-mode');
      
      if (selectedMode === 'roster') {
        if (searchMode !== 'roster') {
          searchMode = 'roster';
          resetAllSelections();
          sel.talent = '__ALL_TALENTS__';
          editing = false;
          updateModeToggleIcon();
        }
        closeModeMenu();
        renderAll();
        document.querySelector('.shell')?.scrollTo({top:0, behavior:'smooth'});
      } else if (selectedMode === 'estimate') {
        if (searchMode !== 'estimate') {
          searchMode = 'estimate';
          resetAllSelections();
          updateModeToggleIcon();
        }
        closeModeMenu();
        document.querySelector('.shell')?.scrollTo({top:0, behavior:'smooth'});
      } else {
        // Per talent e brand, cambia la modalit√† di ricerca
        if (selectedMode !== searchMode) {
          searchMode = selectedMode;
          resetAllSelections();
          updateModeToggleIcon();
        }
        closeModeMenu();
        
        // Scroll to top
        document.querySelector('.shell')?.scrollTo({top:0, behavior:'smooth'});
      }
    });
  });
}

// Chiudi il menu quando clicchi il bottone X
if (els.btnCloseModeMenu) {
  els.btnCloseModeMenu.addEventListener('click', closeModeMenu);
}

// Chiudi il menu quando clicchi sull'overlay
if (els.modeMenuModalOverlay) {
  els.modeMenuModalOverlay.addEventListener('click', closeModeMenu);
}

document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
  if (e.key === 'Escape') {
    if (els.rosterChartModal && els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('open')) {
      closeRosterChartModal();
      return;
    }
    if (els.modeMenuModal && els.modeMenuModal.classList.contains('open')) {
      closeModeMenu();
    }
    return;
  }
  if (e.key !== 'ArrowLeft' && e.key !== 'ArrowRight') return;
  if (!els.rosterChartModal || !els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('open')) return;
  if (!els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('zoomed')) return;
  e.preventDefault();
  stepRosterChartNav(e.key === 'ArrowLeft' ? -1 : 1);
});

function getRosterDownloadLinksForSelection() {
  if (!sel.talent || sel.talent === '__ALL_TALENTS__') {
    return { links: ROSTER_DOWNLOAD_LINKS, label: 'Roster completo' };
  }
  const key = safeSvgId(sel.talent);
  const links = ROSTER_TALENT_DOWNLOAD_LINKS[key];
  if (!links) return null;
  return { links, label: `Scheda di ${prettyLabel(sel.talent)}` };
}

function openRosterDownloadModal() {
  if (!els.rosterDownloadModal || !els.rosterDownloadOverlay) return;
  const ctx = getRosterDownloadLinksForSelection();
  if (!ctx) {
    setStateMessage(`Nessun PDF disponibile per ${prettyLabel(sel.talent)}.`, 'error');
    return;
  }
  currentRosterDownloadLinks = ctx.links;
  const titleEl = document.querySelector('.roster-download-title');
  if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = `Scegli la versione ¬∑ ${ctx.label}`;
  els.rosterDownloadOverlay.classList.add('open');
  els.rosterDownloadModal.classList.add('open');
}

function toDriveDirectUrl(url) {
  const raw = String(url || '');
  if (!raw) return '';
  if (raw.includes('drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=')) return raw;
  const idMatch = raw.match(/\/d\/([^/]+)/) || raw.match(/[?&]id=([^&]+)/);
  const id = idMatch ? idMatch[1] : '';
  if (!id) return raw;
  return `https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=${id}`;
}

function closeRosterDownloadModal() {
  if (!els.rosterDownloadModal || !els.rosterDownloadOverlay) return;
  els.rosterDownloadOverlay.classList.remove('open');
  els.rosterDownloadModal.classList.remove('open');
}

if (els.rosterDownloadBtn) {
  els.rosterDownloadBtn.addEventListener('click', openRosterDownloadModal);
}

if (els.rosterDownloadOverlay) {
  els.rosterDownloadOverlay.addEventListener('click', closeRosterDownloadModal);
}

if (els.rosterDownloadClose) {
  els.rosterDownloadClose.addEventListener('click', closeRosterDownloadModal);
}

document.querySelectorAll('[data-roster-download]').forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const key = btn.getAttribute('data-roster-download');
    const url = currentRosterDownloadLinks ? currentRosterDownloadLinks[key] : '';
    if (url) {
      window.open(toDriveDirectUrl(url), '_blank', 'noopener');
    }
    closeRosterDownloadModal();
  });
});

const ROSTER_CHART_PLATFORMS = [
  {
    key: 'INSTAGRAM',
    label: 'Instagram',
    color: '#DD2A7B',
    gradient: [
      { offset: '0%', color: '#F58529' },
      { offset: '50%', color: '#DD2A7B' },
      { offset: '100%', color: '#8134AF' }
    ]
  },
  {
    key: 'TIKTOK',
    label: 'TikTok',
    color: '#0B0B0B',
    dualGlow: ['#25F4EE', '#FE2C55'],
    pointStroke: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.35)',
    noGlow: true
  },
  {
    key: 'YOUTUBE',
    label: 'YouTube',
    color: '#FF0000',
    gradient: [
      { offset: '0%', color: '#FF0000' },
      { offset: '100%', color: '#FF4D4D' }
    ]
  }
];

function buildRosterChartCards(rows, talentName, onlyPlatform){
  const seriesByPlat = buildRosterSeries(rows);
  const availablePlatforms = ROSTER_CHART_PLATFORMS
    .map(p => p.key)
    .filter(key => (seriesByPlat[key] || []).length);
  const safeSeedBase = safeSvgId(talentName || 'roster');
  const platforms = onlyPlatform
    ? ROSTER_CHART_PLATFORMS.filter(p => p.key === onlyPlatform)
    : ROSTER_CHART_PLATFORMS;
  const cardItems = platforms.map(p => {
    const points = seriesByPlat[p.key] || [];
    if (!points.length) return '';
    const lastVal = points[points.length - 1]?.value;
    const valueLabel = Number.isFinite(lastVal) ? formatFollowersCompactByPlatform(lastVal, p.key) : 'N/A';
    const labels = points.map(pt => pt.label);
    const labelCount = labels.length;
    const labelPositions = labelCount === 1
      ? [50]
      : labels.map((_, i) => {
          const w = 320;
          const pad = 3;
          const step = (w - pad * 2) / (labelCount - 1);
          const x = pad + i * step;
          return (x / w) * 100;
        });
    const labelsHtml = labels.map((l, i) => {
      const left = labelPositions[i] ?? 0;
      return `<span style="left:${left.toFixed(2)}%">${esc(l)}</span>`;
    }).join('');
    const svg = buildRosterChartSvg(points, p, `${p.key}-${safeSeedBase}`);
    const borderColor = hexToRgba(p.color, 0.35);
    const isTiktok = p.key === 'TIKTOK';
    const cardClass = `roster-chart-card${isTiktok ? ' tiktok' : ''}`;
    const borderStyle = isTiktok ? '' : ` style="border-color:${borderColor};"`;
    const chartAttrs = talentName
      ? ` data-roster-chart-talent="${escAttr(talentName)}" data-roster-chart-platform="${escAttr(p.key)}"`
      : '';
    return `
      <div class="${cardClass}"${borderStyle}${chartAttrs}>
        <div class="roster-chart-card-header">
          <span>${esc(p.label)}</span>
          <span class="roster-chart-value" style="display:none;">${esc(valueLabel)}</span>
        </div>
        ${svg}
        <div class="roster-chart-labels">${labelsHtml}</div>
      </div>
    `;
  });
  const visibleCards = cardItems.filter(Boolean);
  return { cardsHtml: visibleCards.join(''), count: visibleCards.length, availablePlatforms };
}

const rosterChartNavState = {
  talent: null,
  platforms: [],
  index: -1
};

function updateRosterChartNav(talentName, platforms, activeKey){
  rosterChartNavState.talent = talentName || null;
  rosterChartNavState.platforms = Array.isArray(platforms) ? platforms : [];
  rosterChartNavState.index = rosterChartNavState.platforms.indexOf(activeKey);
  const hasPrev = rosterChartNavState.index > 0;
  const hasNext = rosterChartNavState.index > -1 && rosterChartNavState.index < rosterChartNavState.platforms.length - 1;
  if (els.rosterChartPrev) {
    els.rosterChartPrev.disabled = !hasPrev;
    els.rosterChartPrev.setAttribute('aria-hidden', (!hasPrev).toString());
  }
  if (els.rosterChartNext) {
    els.rosterChartNext.disabled = !hasNext;
    els.rosterChartNext.setAttribute('aria-hidden', (!hasNext).toString());
  }
}

function resetRosterChartNav(){
  rosterChartNavState.talent = null;
  rosterChartNavState.platforms = [];
  rosterChartNavState.index = -1;
  if (els.rosterChartPrev) {
    els.rosterChartPrev.disabled = true;
    els.rosterChartPrev.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
  }
  if (els.rosterChartNext) {
    els.rosterChartNext.disabled = true;
    els.rosterChartNext.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
  }
}

function stepRosterChartNav(direction){
  if (!rosterChartNavState.talent) return;
  const nextIndex = rosterChartNavState.index + direction;
  if (nextIndex < 0 || nextIndex >= rosterChartNavState.platforms.length) return;
  const nextKey = rosterChartNavState.platforms[nextIndex];
  if (!nextKey) return;
  openRosterChartModal(rosterChartNavState.talent, nextKey);
}

function openRosterChartModal(talentName, onlyPlatform){
  if (!els.rosterChartModal || !els.rosterChartOverlay || !els.rosterChartContent || !els.rosterChartTitle) return;
  const rows = getRosterRowsForTalent(talentName);
  const { cardsHtml, count, availablePlatforms } = buildRosterChartCards(rows, talentName, onlyPlatform);
  const cards = cardsHtml;

  els.rosterChartTitle.textContent = '';
  els.rosterChartContent.innerHTML = cards || `<div class="roster-empty">Nessun dato disponibile.</div>`;
  els.rosterChartContent.classList.toggle('three-cols', count === 3);
  els.rosterChartContent.classList.toggle('one-col', count === 1);
  els.rosterChartModal.classList.toggle('zoomed', Boolean(onlyPlatform));
  els.rosterChartOverlay.classList.add('open');
  els.rosterChartModal.classList.add('open');
  if (onlyPlatform) {
    updateRosterChartNav(talentName, availablePlatforms, onlyPlatform);
    requestAnimationFrame(positionRosterChartClose);
  } else {
    resetRosterChartNav();
    resetRosterChartClosePosition();
  }
}

function closeRosterChartModal(){
  if (!els.rosterChartModal || !els.rosterChartOverlay) return;
  els.rosterChartOverlay.classList.remove('open');
  els.rosterChartModal.classList.remove('open');
  els.rosterChartModal.classList.remove('zoomed');
  resetRosterChartClosePosition();
  resetRosterChartNav();
}

if (els.rosterChartClose) {
  els.rosterChartClose.addEventListener('click', closeRosterChartModal);
}

if (els.rosterChartOverlay) {
  els.rosterChartOverlay.addEventListener('click', closeRosterChartModal);
}

if (els.rosterChartPrev) {
  els.rosterChartPrev.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    e.stopPropagation();
    stepRosterChartNav(-1);
  });
}

if (els.rosterChartNext) {
  els.rosterChartNext.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    e.stopPropagation();
    stepRosterChartNav(1);
  });
}

function positionRosterChartClose(){
  if (!els.rosterChartModal || !els.rosterChartClose) return;
  if (!els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('zoomed')) return;
  const card = els.rosterChartModal.querySelector('.roster-chart-card');
  if (!card) return;
  const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
  const btn = els.rosterChartClose;
  const offset = 4;
  const btnWidth = btn.offsetWidth || 32;
  const btnHeight = btn.offsetHeight || 32;
  const top = Math.max(rect.top + offset, 6);
  const left = Math.min(rect.right - btnWidth - offset, window.innerWidth - btnWidth - 8);
  btn.style.position = 'fixed';
  btn.style.top = `${top}px`;
  btn.style.left = `${left}px`;
  btn.style.right = 'auto';
  btn.style.bottom = 'auto';
  btn.style.zIndex = '2002';
  btn.style.transform = 'none';
}

function resetRosterChartClosePosition(){
  if (!els.rosterChartClose) return;
  const btn = els.rosterChartClose;
  btn.style.position = '';
  btn.style.top = '';
  btn.style.left = '';
  btn.style.right = '';
  btn.style.bottom = '';
  btn.style.zIndex = '';
  btn.style.transform = '';
}

if (els.rosterChartModal) {
  els.rosterChartModal.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (!els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('zoomed')) return;
    if (e.target.closest('.roster-chart-card')) return;
    if (e.target.closest('.roster-chart-nav')) return;
    if (e.target.closest('#rosterChartClose')) return;
    closeRosterChartModal();
  });
}

window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
  if (!els.rosterChartModal) return;
  if (!els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('open')) return;
  if (!els.rosterChartModal.classList.contains('zoomed')) return;
  positionRosterChartClose();
});

document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
  const btn = e.target.closest('[data-roster-chart]');
  if (btn) {
    const talent = btn.getAttribute('data-roster-chart');
    if (talent) openRosterChartModal(talent);
    return;
  }

  const chartCard = e.target.closest('[data-roster-chart-platform]');
  if (!chartCard || chartCard.closest('.roster-chart-modal')) return;
  const talent = chartCard.getAttribute('data-roster-chart-talent');
  const platform = chartCard.getAttribute('data-roster-chart-platform');
  if (!talent || !platform) return;
  openRosterChartModal(talent, platform);
});

document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
  const selectBtn = e.target.closest('[data-growth-select]');
  if (selectBtn) {
    const wrap = selectBtn.closest('.roster-growth-wrap');
    const period = selectBtn.getAttribute('data-growth-select');
    if (period) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.roster-growth').forEach(el => applyRosterGrowthPeriod(el, period));
    }
    document.querySelectorAll('.roster-growth-wrap.open').forEach(el => el.classList.remove('open'));
    return;
  }

  const growthEl = e.target.closest('.roster-growth');
  if (growthEl) {
    const wrap = growthEl.closest('.roster-growth-wrap');
    if (!wrap) return;
    document.querySelectorAll('.roster-growth-wrap.open').forEach(el => {
      if (el !== wrap) el.classList.remove('open');
    });
    wrap.classList.toggle('open');
    return;
  }

  document.querySelectorAll('.roster-growth-wrap.open').forEach(el => el.classList.remove('open'));
});

const rosterWallEl = document.getElementById('roster');
if (rosterWallEl) {
  rosterWallEl.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (searchMode !== 'roster') return;

    const backBtn = e.target.closest('[data-roster-back]');
    if (backBtn) {
      e.preventDefault();
      sel.talent = '__ALL_TALENTS__';
      editing = false;
      step = 0;
      renderAll();
      document.querySelector('.shell')?.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
      return;
    }

    const tile = e.target.closest('[data-roster-talent]');
    if (!tile) return;
    e.preventDefault();
    const talent = tile.getAttribute('data-roster-talent');
    if (!talent) return;
    searchMode = 'roster';
    sel.talent = talent;
    editing = false;
    step = 0;
    renderAll();
    document.querySelector('.shell')?.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
  });
}
