    "Giacomo Czerny",
    "Martina Grado",
    "Matteo Pelusi",
    "Sara Di Sturco",
    "Franco Lucia"
  ]
];
const ROSTER_ORDER = [].concat(...ROSTER_WALL_ROWS);

function buildRosterVocab(){
  if (!Array.isArray(FOLLOWERS)) FOLLOWERS = [];
  const names = new Set();
  FOLLOWERS.forEach(r => {
    const n = String(r['NOME TALENT']||r['TALENT']||r['NOME']||r['NAME']||'').trim();
    if (n) names.add(toTitleCase(n));
  });
  const orderMap = new Map(
    ROSTER_ORDER.map((name, idx) => [normRosterName(name), idx])
  );
  ROSTER_TALENTS = Array.from(names).sort((a,b)=>{
    const aKey = orderMap.get(normRosterName(a));
    const bKey = orderMap.get(normRosterName(b));
    if (aKey != null && bKey != null) return aKey - bKey;
    if (aKey != null) return -1;
    if (bKey != null) return 1;
    return a.localeCompare(b);
  });
}

function rosterPhotoSrc(name){
  return `assets/roster/${safeSvgId(name)}.webp`;
}

let rosterPreloadDone = false;
function preloadRosterImages(){
  if (rosterPreloadDone) return;
  rosterPreloadDone = true;

  const urls = Array.from(new Set(ROSTER_ORDER.map(rosterPhotoSrc)));
  if (!urls.length) return;

  const schedule = (cb) => {
    if (typeof requestIdleCallback === 'function') {
      requestIdleCallback(cb, { timeout: 1200 });
    } else {
      setTimeout(cb, 80);
    }
  };

  let idx = 0;
  const batchSize = 3;
  const loadBatch = () => {
    const end = Math.min(idx + batchSize, urls.length);
    for (; idx < end; idx++) {
      const img = new Image();
      img.decoding = 'async';
      img.src = urls[idx];
    }
    if (idx < urls.length) schedule(loadBatch);
  };

  schedule(loadBatch);
}

function formatFollowersCompact(n){
  const num = Number(String(n).replace(/[^0-9.,]/g,'').replace(/\./g,'').replace(',', '.'));
  if (!Number.isFinite(num)) return 'N/A';
  if (num >= 1_000_000) return (num/1_000_000).toFixed(1).replace(/\.0$/,'') + 'mln';
  if (num >= 1000) return (num/1000).toFixed(1).replace(/\.0$/,'') + 'k';
  return String(Math.round(num));
}

function formatFollowersCompactByPlatform(n, platformKey){
  const num = Number(String(n).replace(/[^0-9.,]/g,'').replace(/\./g,'').replace(',', '.'));
  if (!Number.isFinite(num)) return 'N/A';
  const p = String(platformKey || '').toUpperCase();
  const isYoutube = p === 'YOUTUBE';
  if (num >= 1_000_000) {
    const digits = isYoutube ? 2 : 1;
    let str = (num/1_000_000).toFixed(digits);
    if (isYoutube) {
      str = str.replace(/\.?0+$/,'');
    } else {
      str = str.replace(/\.0$/,'');
    }
    return `${str}mln`;
  }
  if (num >= 1000) return (num/1000).toFixed(1).replace(/\.0$/,'') + 'k';
  return String(Math.round(num));
}

function splitCompactLabel(label){
  const m = String(label).match(/^(.+?)(mln|k)$/i);
  if (!m) return { value: label, unit: '' };
  return { value: m[1], unit: m[2] };
}

function getRosterRowsForTalent(talentName){
  if (!talentName) return [];
  let rows = FOLLOWERS.filter(r => normRosterName(String(r['NOME TALENT']||r['TALENT']||r['NOME']||r['NAME']||'')) === normRosterName(talentName));
  if (rows.length === 0){
    const anyRow = DATA.find(r => norm(String(r[COLS.talent]||'')) === norm(talentName));
    const handle = anyRow ? (anyRow['HANDLE']||anyRow['USERNAME']||anyRow['IG HANDLE']||anyRow['IG']||'') : '';
    if (handle) {
      rows = FOLLOWERS.filter(r => norm(String(r['HANDLE']||r['USERNAME']||r['ACCOUNT']||'')) === norm(handle));
    }
  }
  return rows;
}

function getRosterSocialLink(talentName, platform){
  if (!talentName || !platform) return '';
  const key = safeSvgId(talentName);
  const links = ROSTER_SOCIAL_LINKS[key];
  if (!links) return '';
  return links[platform] || '';
}

function parseFollowersValue(v){
  const num = Number(String(v ?? '').replace(/[^0-9.,]/g,'').replace(/\./g,'').replace(',', '.'));
  return Number.isFinite(num) ? num : null;
}

function hexToRgba(hex, alpha){
  const h = String(hex || '').replace('#','').trim();
  if (h.length !== 6) return `rgba(255,255,255,${alpha})`;
  const r = parseInt(h.slice(0,2), 16);
  const g = parseInt(h.slice(2,4), 16);
  const b = parseInt(h.slice(4,6), 16);
  if (![r,g,b].every(n => Number.isFinite(n))) return `rgba(255,255,255,${alpha})`;
  return `rgba(${r},${g},${b},${alpha})`;
}

function normalizePlatform(raw){
  const p = String(raw || '').toUpperCase();
  if (!p) return '';
  if (p.includes('INSTAGRAM') || p === 'IG') return 'INSTAGRAM';
  if (p.includes('TIKTOK') || p === 'TT') return 'TIKTOK';
  if (p.includes('YOUTUBE') || p === 'YT' || p.includes('SUBSCR')) return 'YOUTUBE';
  return p;
}

function monthKeyFromTs(ts){
  const d = new Date(ts);
  const y = d.getFullYear();
  const m = String(d.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');
  return `${y}-${m}`;
}

function monthLabelFromKey(key){
  const parts = String(key).split('-');
  if (parts.length !== 2) return key;
  const y = parts[0].slice(2);
  return `${parts[1]}/${y}`;
}

function monthFullLabelFromKey(key){
  const parts = String(key).split('-');
  if (parts.length !== 2) return key;
  const year = parts[0];
  const monthNum = parseInt(parts[1], 10);
  if (!Number.isFinite(monthNum) || monthNum < 1 || monthNum > 12) return key;
  const raw = MONTHS_CANONICAL[monthNum - 1] || '';
  const name = raw.replace(/^\d{2}\s*-\s*/,'').trim();
  return year ? `${name} ${year}` : name;
}

function buildRosterSeries(rows){
  const byPlatform = new Map();
  rows.forEach(r => {
    const plat = normalizePlatform(r['PIATTAFORMA']||r['PLATFORM']||r['PIATTA']||r['SOCIAL']||'');
    if (!plat) return;
    const dateRaw = r['DATA']||r['DATE']||r['AGGIORNATO']||r['UPDATED']||'';
    const ts = parseItalianDate(dateRaw);
    if (!ts) return;
    const valRaw = r['FOLLOWERS']||r['VALORE']||r['COUNT']||r['FANS']||r['ISCRITTI']||r['SUBSCRIBERS']||r['FOLLOWER'];
    const val = parseFollowersValue(valRaw);
    if (!Number.isFinite(val)) return;
    const key = monthKeyFromTs(ts);
    let map = byPlatform.get(plat);
    if (!map) { map = new Map(); byPlatform.set(plat, map); }
    const prev = map.get(key);
    if (!prev || ts > prev.ts){
      map.set(key, { ts, val });
    }
  });

  const out = {};
  byPlatform.forEach((map, plat) => {
    const keys = Array.from(map.keys()).sort();
    const lastKeys = keys.slice(-12);
    const points = lastKeys.map(k => ({ label: monthLabelFromKey(k), value: map.get(k).val }));
    out[plat] = points;
  });
  return out;
}

function buildRosterChartSvg(points, style, idSeed){
  const width = 320;
  const height = 200;
  const padX = 3;
  const padY = 8;
  const w = width - padX * 2;
  const h = height - padY * 2;
  const vals = points.map(p => p.value).filter(Number.isFinite);
  if (!vals.length) return '';
  let min = Math.min(...vals);
  let max = Math.max(...vals);
  if (min === max) { min -= 1; max += 1; }
  const range = max - min;
  const padRange = range * 0.12;
  min -= padRange;
  max += padRange;
  const step = points.length > 1 ? (w / (points.length - 1)) : 0;
  const coords = points.map((p, i) => {
    const x = padX + i * step;
    const t = (p.value - min) / (max - min);
    const y = padY + (1 - t) * h;
    return { x, y };
  });
  const line = coords.map(c => `${c.x.toFixed(1)},${c.y.toFixed(1)}`).join(' ');
  const area = [
    `M ${coords[0].x.toFixed(1)} ${coords[0].y.toFixed(1)}`,
    ...coords.slice(1).map(c => `L ${c.x.toFixed(1)} ${c.y.toFixed(1)}`),
    `L ${coords[coords.length - 1].x.toFixed(1)} ${(height - padY).toFixed(1)}`,
    `L ${coords[0].x.toFixed(1)} ${(height - padY).toFixed(1)}`,
    'Z'
  ].join(' ');
  const safeSeed = safeSvgId(idSeed || 'chart');
  const strokeId = `roster-line-${safeSeed}`;
  const fillId = `roster-fill-${safeSeed}`;
  const glowId = `roster-glow-${safeSeed}`;
  const softGlowId = `roster-soft-${safeSeed}`;
  const gradientStops = (style.gradient || []).map(s => `<stop offset="${s.offset}" stop-color="${s.color}"></stop>`).join('');
  const fillStops = (style.gradient || []).map(s => `<stop offset="${s.offset}" stop-color="${s.color}" stop-opacity="0.35"></stop>`).join('');
  const strokeRef = style.gradient ? `url(#${strokeId})` : style.color;
  const fillRef = style.gradient ? `url(#${fillId})` : hexToRgba(style.color, 0.2);
  const pointStroke = style.pointStroke || 'rgba(255,255,255,0.6)';
  const mainFilter = style.noGlow ? '' : `filter="url(#${glowId})"`;
  const pointsMarkup = coords.map((c, i) => {
    const raw = points[i]?.value;
    const label = Number.isFinite(raw) ? formatFollowersCompactByPlatform(raw, style.key) : 'N/A';
    const parts = splitCompactLabel(label);
    let y = c.y - 14;
    if (y < 6) y = 6;
    let anchor = 'middle';
    let dx = 0;
    if (i === 0) { anchor = 'start'; dx = 2; }
    else if (i === coords.length - 1) { anchor = 'end'; dx = -2; }
    const unitHtml = parts.unit ? `<tspan font-size="5" dx="1">${esc(parts.unit)}</tspan>` : '';
    return `
      <g class="roster-point">
        <circle cx="${c.x.toFixed(1)}" cy="${c.y.toFixed(1)}" r="2.1" fill="${style.color}" stroke="${pointStroke}" stroke-width="0.6"></circle>
        <text x="${(c.x + dx).toFixed(1)}" y="${y.toFixed(1)}" text-anchor="${anchor}" font-size="7" fill="rgba(229,231,235,0.85)">${esc(parts.value)}${unitHtml}</text>
      </g>
    `;
  }).join('');
  return `
    <svg class="roster-chart-svg" viewBox="0 0 ${width} ${height}" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
      <defs>
        ${style.gradient ? `
          <linearGradient id="${strokeId}" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
            ${gradientStops}
          </linearGradient>
          <linearGradient id="${fillId}" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
            ${fillStops}
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="${style.color}" stop-opacity="0"></stop>
          </linearGradient>
        ` : ''}
        <filter id="${glowId}" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
          <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="2.4" result="blur"/>
          <feMerge>
            <feMergeNode in="blur"/>
            <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
          </feMerge>
        </filter>
        <filter id="${softGlowId}" x="-30%" y="-30%" width="160%" height="160%">
          <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3.2" result="blur"/>
          <feMerge>
            <feMergeNode in="blur"/>
            <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
          </feMerge>
        </filter>
      </defs>
      <line x1="${padX}" y1="${padY}" x2="${padX}" y2="${height - padY}" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1"></line>
      <line x1="${padX}" y1="${height - padY}" x2="${width - padX}" y2="${height - padY}" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1"></line>
      <path d="${area}" fill="${fillRef}" opacity="0.45"></path>
      ${style.dualGlow ? `
        <polyline fill="none" stroke="${style.dualGlow[0]}" stroke-width="4.4" opacity="0.45" filter="url(#${softGlowId})" points="${line}" transform="translate(-0.6,0.6)"></polyline>
        <polyline fill="none" stroke="${style.dualGlow[1] || style.dualGlow[0]}" stroke-width="4.4" opacity="0.45" filter="url(#${softGlowId})" points="${line}" transform="translate(0.6,-0.6)"></polyline>
      ` : ''}
      <polyline fill="none" stroke="${strokeRef}" stroke-width="2.4" ${mainFilter} points="${line}"></polyline>
      ${pointsMarkup}
    </svg>
  `;
}

function latestByPlatform(rows){
  // Expect columns: PLATFORM/PIATTAFORMA, DATE/DATA, FOLLOWERS
  const byPl = new Map();
  for (const r of rows){
    const plat = String(r['PIATTAFORMA']||r['PLATFORM']||r['PIATTA']||r['SOCIAL']||'').toUpperCase();
    const dateRaw = r['DATA']||r['DATE']||r['AGGIORNATO']||r['UPDATED']||'';
    const ts = parseItalianDate(dateRaw);
    const prev = byPl.get(plat);
    if (!prev || ts > prev.ts){
      byPl.set(plat, { ts, row: r });
    }
  }
  const out = {};
  byPl.forEach(({row}, plat) => {
    const val = row['FOLLOWERS']||row['VALORE']||row['COUNT']||row['FANS']||row['ISCRITTI']||row['SUBSCRIBERS']||row['FOLLOWER'];
    out[plat] = val;
  });
  if (Object.keys(out).length === 0 && rows.length){
    // Fallback: columns per platform on latest-dated row
    const rowsWithTs = rows.map(r => ({ r, ts: parseItalianDate(r['DATA']||r['DATE']||'')})).sort((a,b)=>b.ts-a.ts);
    const latest = rowsWithTs[0]?.r || rows[0];
    const keys = Object.keys(latest||{});
    const mapKey = (pats) => keys.find(k => pats.some(p=>k.toUpperCase().includes(p)));
    const igKey = mapKey(['INSTAGRAM','IG']);
    const ttKey = mapKey(['TIKTOK','TT']);
    const ytKey = mapKey(['YOUTUBE','YT','SUBSCR']);
    if (igKey) out['INSTAGRAM'] = latest[igKey];
    if (ttKey) out['TIKTOK'] = latest[ttKey];
    if (ytKey) out['YOUTUBE'] = latest[ytKey];
  }
  return out;
}

function growthByPlatform(rows){
  const byPl = new Map();
  for (const r of rows){
    const plat = normalizePlatform(r['PIATTAFORMA']||r['PLATFORM']||r['PIATTA']||r['SOCIAL']||'');
    if (!plat) continue;
    const dateRaw = r['DATA']||r['DATE']||r['AGGIORNATO']||r['UPDATED']||'';
    const ts = parseItalianDate(dateRaw);
    if (!ts) continue;
    const valRaw = r['FOLLOWERS']||r['VALORE']||r['COUNT']||r['FANS']||r['ISCRITTI']||r['SUBSCRIBERS']||r['FOLLOWER'];
    const val = parseFollowersValue(valRaw);
    if (!Number.isFinite(val)) continue;
    const key = monthKeyFromTs(ts);
    let map = byPl.get(plat);
    if (!map) { map = new Map(); byPl.set(plat, map); }
    const prev = map.get(key);
    if (!prev || ts > prev.ts){
      map.set(key, { ts, val });
    }
  }
  const out = {};
  byPl.forEach((map, plat) => {
    const keys = Array.from(map.keys()).sort();
    if (keys.length < 2) return;
    const lastKey = keys[keys.length - 1];
    const prevKey = keys[keys.length - 2];
    const lastVal = map.get(lastKey)?.val;
    const prevVal = map.get(prevKey)?.val;
    if (!Number.isFinite(lastVal) || !Number.isFinite(prevVal) || prevVal === 0) return;
    const pct = ((lastVal - prevVal) / prevVal) * 100;
    out[plat] = { pct, prevKey, lastKey };
  });
  return out;
}

function buildRosterPlatformSeries(rows){
  const byPl = new Map();
  for (const r of rows){
    const plat = normalizePlatform(r['PIATTAFORMA']||r['PLATFORM']||r['PIATTA']||r['SOCIAL']||'');
    if (!plat) continue;
    const dateRaw = r['DATA']||r['DATE']||r['AGGIORNATO']||r['UPDATED']||'';
    const ts = parseItalianDate(dateRaw);
    if (!ts) continue;
    const valRaw = r['FOLLOWERS']||r['VALORE']||r['COUNT']||r['FANS']||r['ISCRITTI']||r['SUBSCRIBERS']||r['FOLLOWER'];
    const val = parseFollowersValue(valRaw);
    if (!Number.isFinite(val)) continue;
    const key = monthKeyFromTs(ts);
    let map = byPl.get(plat);
    if (!map) { map = new Map(); byPl.set(plat, map); }
    const prev = map.get(key);
    if (!prev || ts > prev.ts){
      map.set(key, { ts, val, key });
    }
  }
  const out = {};
  byPl.forEach((map, plat) => {
    const keys = Array.from(map.keys()).sort();
    out[plat] = keys.map(k => map.get(k)).sort((a,b)=>a.ts-b.ts);
  });
  return out;
}

function getRosterGrowthOptions(series){
  const out = {};
  if (!Array.isArray(series) || series.length < 2) return out;
  const latest = series[series.length - 1];
  const candidates = series.slice(0, -1);
  const periods = [30, 90, 365];
  periods.forEach(days => {
    const windowStart = latest.ts - (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);
    let ref = null;
    for (let i = 0; i < candidates.length; i++){
      if (candidates[i].ts >= windowStart) { ref = candidates[i]; break; }
    }
    if (!ref) {
      for (let i = candidates.length - 1; i >= 0; i--){
        if (candidates[i].ts < windowStart) { ref = candidates[i]; break; }
      }
    }
    if (!ref || !Number.isFinite(ref.val) || ref.val === 0) return;
    const pct = ((latest.val - ref.val) / ref.val) * 100;
    out[days] = {
      pct,
      refLabel: monthFullLabelFromKey(ref.key)
    };
  });
  return out;
}

function buildGrowthTooltipText(pct, refLabel){
  const compareLabel = refLabel ? `rispetto a ${refLabel}` : 'rispetto al periodo selezionato';
  if (pct === 0) return `Stabile ${compareLabel}`;
  const dirLabel = pct > 0 ? 'Aumento' : 'Diminuzione';
  return `${dirLabel} del ${formatGrowthPercent(pct)}% ${compareLabel}`;
}

function applyRosterGrowthPeriod(el, period){
  if (!el) return;
  let pctRaw = el.dataset[`growth${period}`];
  let refLabel = el.dataset[`growthRef${period}`] || '';
  if (!pctRaw || !Number.isFinite(parseFloat(pctRaw))) {
    const talent = el.dataset.growthTalent || sel.talent || '';
    const platform = el.dataset.growthPlatform || '';
    const rows = getRosterRowsForTalent(talent);
    const seriesByPlat = buildRosterPlatformSeries(rows);
    const series = seriesByPlat[platform] || [];
    const options = getRosterGrowthOptions(series);
    const opt = options[period];
    if (opt && Number.isFinite(opt.pct)) {
      pctRaw = String(opt.pct);
      refLabel = opt.refLabel || '';
    }
  }
  const valueEl = el.querySelector('.roster-growth-value');
  const arrowEl = el.querySelector('.roster-growth-arrow');
  el.dataset.growthPeriod = period;
  el.classList.remove('up', 'down', 'empty');
  if (!pctRaw || !Number.isFinite(parseFloat(pctRaw))) {
    el.classList.add('empty');
    if (valueEl) valueEl.textContent = '‚Äî';
    if (arrowEl) arrowEl.textContent = '';
    el.removeAttribute('data-tooltip');
    return;
  }
  const pct = parseFloat(pctRaw);
  const isUp = pct >= 0;
  el.classList.add(isUp ? 'up' : 'down');
  const sign = pct > 0 ? '+' : '';
  if (valueEl) valueEl.textContent = `${sign}${formatGrowthPercent(pct)}%`;
  if (arrowEl) arrowEl.textContent = isUp ? '‚Üë' : '‚Üì';
  el.dataset.tooltip = buildGrowthTooltipText(pct, refLabel);
}

function formatGrowthPercent(value){
  const abs = Math.abs(value);
  const fixed = abs.toFixed(1);
  const trimmed = fixed.endsWith('.0') ? fixed.slice(0, -2) : fixed;
  return trimmed.replace('.', ',');
}

/* ====== HELPERS ====== */
function rowsFiltered() {
  let rows = DATA;
  // Filter order doesn't matter for the result set, only for the UI wizard steps
  if (sel.talent) rows = rows.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent]) === norm(sel.talent));
  rows = filterRowsBySelectedBrand(rows);
  if (sel.year)   rows = rows.filter(r => norm(String(r[COLS.year])) === norm(String(sel.year)));

  if (sel.month && sel.month !== "__ALL_MONTHS__") {
    const targetKey = monthKey(sel.month);
    rows = rows.filter(r => monthKey(r[COLS.month]) === targetKey);
  }

  return rows;
}

function computePeriodLabel(rows){
  const uniqMonthsRaw = uniq(rows.map(r => String(r[COLS.month]||''))).sort((a,b)=>monthKey(a)-monthKey(b));
  const uniqNames = uniqMonthsRaw.map(m => monthName(m));
  if (!uniqMonthsRaw.length) return '‚Äî';
  
  // Logic from renderResults to use full names if <= 2
  const showFullMonth = uniqMonthsRaw.length <= 2;
  
  if (showFullMonth) {
      return uniqMonthsRaw.map(m => {
          const clean = String(m||'').replace(/^\s*\d{1,2}\s*[-‚Äì]\s*/,'').trim();
          return toTitleCase(clean);
      }).join(' ¬∑ ');
  }

  return uniqNames.join(' ¬∑ ');
}

function getPeriodMonths(rows){
  const uniqMonthsRaw = uniq(rows.map(r => String(r[COLS.month]||''))).sort((a,b)=>monthKey(a)-monthKey(b));
  return uniqMonthsRaw.map(m => monthName(m));
}

function computeContentTypesSummary(rows){
  let tiktok = 0, reel = 0, post = 0;
  const igsSets = new Set();
  let igsSingles = 0;

  for (const r of rows){
    const b = getBucket(r[COLS.type]);
    if (b === "TIKTOK") tiktok++;
    else if (b === "REEL") reel++;
    else if (b === "POST") post++;
    else if (b === "IGS"){
      const n = igsSetNum(r[COLS.type]);
      if (n != null) {
        const brandKey = norm(r[COLS.brand]);
        const monthNorm = norm(String(r[COLS.month]));
        const key = `${brandKey}||${monthNorm}||${n}`;
        igsSets.add(key);
      } else {
        // Conteggia anche le IGS singole (non appartenenti ad alcun Set)
        igsSingles++;
      }
    }
  }

  const parts = [];
  if (igsSets.size) parts.push({ bucket:"IGS",    label:`${igsSets.size} IGS Set` });
  if (igsSingles)    parts.push({ bucket:"IGS",    label:`${igsSingles} IGS` });
  if (reel)          parts.push({ bucket:"REEL",   label:`${reel} Reel` });
  if (post)          parts.push({ bucket:"POST",   label:`${post} Post` });
  if (tiktok)        parts.push({ bucket:"TIKTOK", label:`${tiktok} TikTok` });

  const text = parts.map(p => p.label).join(' ¬∑ ');

  // üî¢ totale pubblicazioni: include IGS Set + IGS singole
  const totalPublications = igsSets.size + igsSingles + reel + post + tiktok;

  return {
    text,
    igsSetsCount: igsSets.size,
    parts,
    totalPublications
  };
}

function buildEstimateSnapshot(talentName, limit = 3) {
  if (!talentName) return { rows: [], periodLabels: [] };
  const baseRows = DATA.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent]) === norm(talentName)).filter(r => !r.isAdv);
  if (!baseRows.length) return { rows: [], periodLabels: [] };

  const stamps = Array.from(new Set(baseRows.map(monthStampFromRow).filter(s => Number.isFinite(s))));
  if (!stamps.length) return { rows: [], periodLabels: [] };

  stamps.sort((a, b) => b - a);
  const recent = stamps.slice(0, limit);
  const stampSet = new Set(recent);
  const rows = baseRows.filter(r => stampSet.has(monthStampFromRow(r)));
  const periodLabels = recent.slice().sort((a, b) => a - b).map(labelFromMonthStamp);

  return { rows, periodLabels };
}


/* ====== VOCABOLARI DA DATA ====== */
const TALENT_STOPWORDS = new Set(["di","de","del","della","dello","dei","degli","delle","da","dal","dalla","dallo","dai","dagli","dalle","la","il","lo","le","i","gli","e"]);

function buildVocabs(){
  const talentsRaw = uniq(DATA.map(r => String(r[COLS.talent] || '').trim()));
  TALENT_VOCAB = talentsRaw.map(name => {
    const n = norm(name);
    const words = n.replace(/[.,;:!?]/g,' ').split(/\s+/).filter(Boolean).filter(w => w.length > 2 && !TALENT_STOPWORDS.has(w));
    return { name, norm: n, tokens: words };
  }).sort((a,b)=> b.name.length - a.name.length);

  const brandsRaw = uniq(DATA.map(r => String(r[COLS.brand] || '').trim()));
  const brandBases = uniq(brandsRaw.map(brandBase));
  BRAND_VOCAB = brandBases.map(name => ({ name, norm: norm(name) })).sort((a,b)=> b.norm.length - a.norm.length);
}

/* ====== WIZARD LOGIC UPDATED FOR MODES ====== */
function optionsForStep() {
  /* --- TALENT MODE: Talent -> Year -> Month -> Brand --- */
  if (searchMode === 'talent') {
    if (step===0) {
        const allVals = uniq(DATA.map(r => String(r[COLS.talent] ?? '').trim()));
        let vals = talentSearch.trim() ? allVals.filter(name => norm(name).includes(norm(talentSearch))) : allVals;
        return { title:"Scegli il Talent", items: vals, mode: 'talent' };
    }
    if (step===1) {
        const byT = sel.talent ? DATA.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent])===norm(sel.talent)) : DATA;
        const years = uniq(byT.map(r => String(r[COLS.year] ?? '') )).reverse();
        return { title:"Scegli l'Anno", items: years, mode: 'year' };
    }
    if (step===2) {
        const byT = DATA.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent])===norm(sel.talent));
        const byY = byT.filter(r => norm(String(r[COLS.year]))===norm(String(sel.year)));
        availableMonthKeys = new Set(byY.map(r => monthKey(r[COLS.month])).filter(k => Number.isFinite(k) && k >= 1 && k <= 12));
        return { title:"Scegli il Mese", items: ["__ALL_MONTHS__", ...MONTHS_CANONICAL], mode: 'month' };
    }
    if (step===3) {
        const byT = DATA.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent])===norm(sel.talent));
        const byY = byT.filter(r => norm(String(r[COLS.year]))===norm(String(sel.year)));
        const source = (sel.month === "__ALL_MONTHS__") ? byY : byY.filter(r => monthKey(r[COLS.month]) === monthKey(sel.month));
        const brands = getBrandBases(source);
        return { title:"Scegli l'Attivit√†", items: ["__ALL__", ...brands], mode: 'brand' };
    }
    if (step===4) {
        const source = getTalentBrandSourceRows();
        const campaigns = getBrandCampaigns(source, sel.brand);
        return { title:"Scegli la Campagna", items: campaigns, mode: 'campaign' };
    }
  } 
  /* --- BRAND MODE: Brand -> Talent -> Year -> Month --- */
  else if (searchMode === 'brand') {
    const stepMap = getBrandModeStepMap();
    if (step===0) {
        const allBrands = getBrandBases(DATA);
        let vals = talentSearch.trim() ? allBrands.filter(name => norm(name).includes(norm(talentSearch))) : allBrands;
        return { title:"Scegli l'Attivit√†", items: vals, mode: 'brand' };
    }
    if (stepMap.needsCampaign && step===stepMap.campaign) {
        const campaigns = getBrandCampaigns(DATA, sel.brand);
        return { title:"Scegli la Campagna", items: campaigns, mode: 'campaign' };
    }
    if (step===stepMap.talent) {
        // Filter by Brand (and Campaign if set) -> Show Talents
        const byB = sel.brand ? filterRowsBySelectedBrand(DATA) : DATA;
        const talents = uniq(byB.map(r => String(r[COLS.talent] ?? '').trim()));
        return { title:"Scegli il Talent", items: talents, mode: 'talent' };
    }
    if (step===stepMap.year) {
        // Filter by Brand + Talent -> Show Years
        const byB = filterRowsBySelectedBrand(DATA);
        const byT = byB.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent])===norm(sel.talent));
        const years = uniq(byT.map(r => String(r[COLS.year] ?? '') )).reverse();
        return { title:"Scegli l'Anno", items: years, mode: 'year' };
    }
    if (step===stepMap.month) {
        // Filter by Brand + Talent + Year -> Show Months
        const byB = filterRowsBySelectedBrand(DATA);
        const byT = byB.filter(r => norm(r[COLS.talent])===norm(sel.talent));
        const byY = byT.filter(r => norm(String(r[COLS.year]))===norm(String(sel.year)));
        availableMonthKeys = new Set(byY.map(r => monthKey(r[COLS.month])).filter(k => Number.isFinite(k) && k >= 1 && k <= 12));
        return { title:"Scegli il Mese", items: ["__ALL_MONTHS__", ...MONTHS_CANONICAL], mode: 'month' };
    }
  }
  /* --- ROSTER MODE: Talent (da FOLLOWER) --- */
  else if (searchMode === 'roster') {
    if (step === 0){
      // Primo step: elenco talent dal foglio FOLLOWER (con ricerca)
      const allVals = ROSTER_TALENTS;
      let vals = talentSearch.trim() ? allVals.filter(name => norm(name).includes(norm(talentSearch))) : allVals;
      return { title:"Scegli il Talent", items: vals, mode: 'roster-talent' };
    }
  }
  /* --- ESTIMATE MODE: Talent (da DATA) --- */
  else if (searchMode === 'estimate') {
    if (step === 0) {
      const allVals = uniq(DATA.map(r => String(r[COLS.talent] ?? '').trim()));
      let vals = talentSearch.trim() ? allVals.filter(name => norm(name).includes(norm(talentSearch))) : allVals;
      return { title:"Scegli il Talent", items: vals, mode: 'estimate-talent' };
    }
  }
  return { title:"", items:[], mode:'' };
}

function wireOptionClicks() {
  const btns = els.options.querySelectorAll('.opt[data-value]');
  for (const btn of btns) {
    btn.onclick = () => {
      const v = btn.getAttribute('data-value');

      // LOGICA ROBUSTA: Imposta valore, Pulisci successivi, Avanza Step
      if (searchMode === 'talent') {
          if (step === 0) {
              sel.talent = v;
              sel.year = ""; sel.month = ""; sel.brand = ""; sel.campaign = ""; // Clear next
              step = 1;
          } else if (step === 1) {
              sel.year = v;
              sel.month = ""; sel.brand = ""; sel.campaign = ""; // Clear next
              step = 2;
          } else if (step === 2) {
              sel.month = v;
              sel.brand = ""; sel.campaign = ""; // Clear next
              step = 3;
          } else if (step === 3) {
              sel.brand = v;
              sel.campaign = "";
              if (v === "__ALL__") {
                editing = false;
              } else if (talentBrandHasCampaigns(v)) {
                step = 4;
              } else {
                editing = false;
              }
          } else if (step === 4) {
              sel.campaign = v;
              // Ultimo step: non pulisco nulla, non avanzo step, chiudo editing
              editing = false;
          }
        } else if (searchMode === 'brand') {
          // BRAND MODE
          const stepMap = getBrandModeStepMap();
          if (step === 0) {
              sel.brand = v;
              sel.campaign = "";
              sel.talent = ""; sel.year = ""; sel.month = ""; // Clear next
              step = 1;
          } else if (stepMap.needsCampaign && step === stepMap.campaign) {
              sel.campaign = v;
              sel.talent = ""; sel.year = ""; sel.month = "";
              step = stepMap.talent;
          } else if (step === stepMap.talent) {
              sel.talent = v;
              sel.year = ""; sel.month = "";
              step = stepMap.year;
          } else if (step === stepMap.year) {
              sel.year = v;
              sel.month = "";
              step = stepMap.month;
          } else if (step === stepMap.month) {
              sel.month = v;
              // Ultimo step
              editing = false;
          }
        } else if (searchMode === 'roster') {
          // ROSTER MODE: un solo step per ora (selezione talent) -> mostra risultati
          if (step === 0) {
            sel.talent = v;
            editing = false;
          }
        } else if (searchMode === 'estimate') {
          // ESTIMATE MODE: un solo step (selezione talent)
          if (step === 0) {
            sel.talent = v;
            editing = false;
          }
        }

      renderAll();
      // Renderizza ancora il wizard se non abbiamo finito (cio√® se editing √® ancora true)
      if (editing) renderWizard(); 
    };
  }
}


function renderWizard() {
  const meta = optionsForStep();
  let html = '';

  // --- TALENT / BRAND con barra di ricerca al primo step ---
  if (meta.mode === 'talent' || meta.mode === 'brand' || meta.mode === 'campaign' || meta.mode === 'roster-talent' || meta.mode === 'estimate-talent') {

    // Caso speciale: step finale in modalit√† TALENT (brand + "Tutte le attivit√†")
    const isFinalTalentBrandStep =
      (searchMode === 'talent' && meta.mode === 'brand' && step === 3);

    if (isFinalTalentBrandStep) {
      // Step finale in modalit√† TALENT: bottone "Tutte le attivit√†" + brand singoli
      const allBtn = `<button class="opt full-width" data-value="__ALL__">Tutte le attivit√†</button>`;
      const brandButtons = meta.items
        .filter(v => v !== "__ALL__")
        .map(v => `<button class="opt" data-value="${escAttr(v)}">${esc(prettyLabel(v))}</button>`)
        .join('');

      html = `
        <div class="options-container">
          ${allBtn}
          <div class="grid-content">${brandButtons}</div>
        </div>`;
    } else {
      // Logica normale: primo step con barra di ricerca, passi successivi solo bottoni
      const isFirstStep = (step === 0);
      if (isFirstStep) {
        const btnHtml = meta.items.map(v =>
          `<button class="opt" data-value="${escAttr(v)}">${esc(prettyLabel(v))}</button>`
        ).join('');

        const ph = (meta.mode === 'talent' || meta.mode === 'roster-talent' || meta.mode === 'estimate-talent')
          ? "Cerca talent..."
          : "Cerca attivit√†...";

        html = `
          <div class="options-container">
            <div class="search-card opt">
              <span class="search-icon">üîç</span>
              <input id="wizardSearchInput" class="search-input" type="text"
                     value="${escAttr(talentSearch)}"
                     placeholder="${ph}"/>
            </div>
            <div id="optionsList" class="grid-content">
              ${btnHtml || '<div class="muted" style="text-align:center;width:100%;padding:16px;">Nessun risultato.</div>'}
            </div>
          </div>`;
      } else {
        const btnHtml = meta.items.map(v =>
          `<button class="opt" data-value="${escAttr(v)}">${esc(prettyLabel(v))}</button>`
        ).join('') || '<div class="muted" style="text-align:center;width:100%;padding:16px;">Nessun risultato.</div>';

        html = `
          <div class="options-container">
            <div class="grid-content">${btnHtml}</div>
          </div>`;
      }
    }
  } else if (meta.mode === 'year') {
    // Anni: bottoni full-width
    const yearButtonsHtml = meta.items
      .map(v => `<button class="opt full-width" data-value="${escAttr(v)}">${esc(v)}</button>`)
      .join('');
    html = `<div class="options-container">${yearButtonsHtml}</div>`;

  } else if (meta.mode === 'month') {
    // Mesi: "Tutto l‚Äôanno" + griglia 4 colonne
    const allMonthsButton = `<button class="opt full-width" data-value="__ALL_MONTHS__">Tutto l‚Äôanno</button>`;
    const monthButtons = MONTHS_CANONICAL.map(v => {
      const k = monthKey(v);
      const isDisabled = !availableMonthKeys.has(k);
      const disabledClass = isDisabled ? " disabled" : "";
      const dataValueAttr = isDisabled ? "" : ` data-value="${escAttr(v)}"`;
      return `<button class="opt${disabledClass}"${dataValueAttr}>${esc(monthName(v))}</button>`;
    }).join('');
    html = `
      <div class="options-container">
        ${allMonthsButton}
        <div class="grid-content months">${monthButtons}</div>
      </div>`;
  }

  // Inserisco HTML nel pannello
  els.options.innerHTML = html;

  // --- Search input (se presente) ---
  const inp  = document.getElementById('wizardSearchInput');
  const list = document.getElementById('optionsList');
  if (inp && list) {
    inp.oninput = (e) => {
      talentSearch = e.target.value || "";
      const metaNow = optionsForStep();
      const newListHtml = metaNow.items.map(v =>
        `<button class="opt" data-value="${escAttr(v)}">${esc(prettyLabel(v))}</button>`
      ).join('');
      list.innerHTML = newListHtml;
      wireOptionClicks();
    };
    inp.focus();
  }

  // Aggancio i click sui bottoni delle opzioni
  wireOptionClicks();

  /* --- BREADCRUMBS RENDERING --- */
  const monthLabel = sel.month === "__ALL_MONTHS__"
    ? "Tutto l‚Äôanno"
    : (sel.month ? monthName(sel.month) : 'Mese');

  const brandLabel = sel.brand === "__ALL__"
    ? "Tutte le attivit√†"
    : (sel.brand ? prettyLabel(brandBase(sel.brand)) : 'Attivit√†');
  const campaignLabel = sel.campaign ? prettyLabel(sel.campaign) : 'Campagna';

  const talentLabel = sel.talent ? prettyLabel(sel.talent) : 'Talent';
  const yearLabel = sel.year || 'Anno';

  const chip = (label, isSet, jumpIndex) =>
    `<span class="chip btn ${isSet?'sel':''} ${isSet?'':'disabled'}" data-jump="${jumpIndex}">${label}</span>`;

  let crumbsHtml = '';
  if (searchMode === 'talent') {
    // Talent ‚Üí Year ‚Üí Month ‚Üí Brand ‚Üí Campaign (se presente)
    const showCampaign = !!sel.brand && sel.brand !== "__ALL__" && talentBrandHasCampaigns(sel.brand);
    const baseCrumbs = [
      chip(talentLabel, !!sel.talent, 0),
      chip(yearLabel,   !!sel.year,   1),
      chip(monthLabel,  !!sel.month,  2),
      chip(brandLabel,  !!sel.brand,  3)
    ];
    if (showCampaign) baseCrumbs.push(chip(campaignLabel, !!sel.campaign, 4));
    crumbsHtml = baseCrumbs.join('');
  } else if (searchMode === 'brand') {
    // Brand ‚Üí (Campaign) ‚Üí Talent ‚Üí Year ‚Üí Month
    const stepMap = getBrandModeStepMap();
    const baseCrumbs = [
      chip(brandLabel,  !!sel.brand,  stepMap.brand)
    ];
    if (stepMap.needsCampaign) {
      baseCrumbs.push(chip(campaignLabel, !!sel.campaign, stepMap.campaign));
    }
    baseCrumbs.push(
      chip(talentLabel, !!sel.talent, stepMap.talent),
      chip(yearLabel,   !!sel.year,   stepMap.year),
      chip(monthLabel,  !!sel.month,  stepMap.month)
    );
    crumbsHtml = baseCrumbs.join('');
  } else if (searchMode === 'roster') {
    crumbsHtml = [ chip(talentLabel, !!sel.talent, 0) ].join('');
  } else if (searchMode === 'estimate') {
    crumbsHtml = [ chip(talentLabel, !!sel.talent, 0) ].join('');
  }
  els.crumbs.innerHTML = crumbsHtml;

  // Click sui breadcrumb: reset solo da quel punto in avanti
  for (const c of els.crumbs.querySelectorAll('.chip.btn')) {
    c.onclick = () => {
      const jump = parseInt(c.dataset.jump, 10);
      if (Number.isNaN(jump)) return;

      editing = true;

      if (searchMode === 'talent') {
        // Ordine: 0 Talent ‚Üí 1 Anno ‚Üí 2 Mese ‚Üí 3 Brand ‚Üí 4 Campagna
        if (jump <= 0) {
          // Clic su Talent: cancella tutto
          sel.talent = "";
          sel.year   = "";
          sel.month  = "";
          sel.brand  = "";
          sel.campaign = "";
        } else if (jump === 1) {
          // Clic su Anno: tengo Talent, azzero da Anno in gi√π
          sel.year   = "";
          sel.month  = "";
          sel.brand  = "";
          sel.campaign = "";
        } else if (jump === 2) {
          // Clic su Mese: tengo Talent+Anno, azzero Mese+Brand
          sel.month  = "";
          sel.brand  = "";
          sel.campaign = "";
        } else if (jump === 3) {
          // Clic su Brand: tengo tutto, azzero Brand + Campagna
          sel.brand  = "";
          sel.campaign = "";
        } else if (jump === 4) {
          // Clic su Campagna: tengo tutto, azzero solo Campagna
          sel.campaign = "";
        }
      } else if (searchMode === 'brand') {
        // BRAND MODE ‚Äî Ordine: 0 Brand ‚Üí 1 Campagna ‚Üí 2 Talent ‚Üí 3 Anno ‚Üí 4 Mese
        const stepMap = getBrandModeStepMap();
        if (jump <= stepMap.brand) {
          // Clic su Brand: cancella tutto
          sel.brand  = "";
          sel.campaign = "";
          sel.talent = "";
          sel.year   = "";
          sel.month  = "";
        } else if (stepMap.needsCampaign && jump === stepMap.campaign) {
          // Clic su Campagna: tengo Brand, azzero Campagna+successivi
          sel.campaign = "";
          sel.talent = "";
          sel.year   = "";
          sel.month  = "";
        } else if (jump === stepMap.talent) {
          // Clic su Talent: tengo Brand (+Campagna), azzero da Talent in gi√π
          sel.talent = "";
          sel.year   = "";
          sel.month  = "";
        } else if (jump === stepMap.year) {
          // Clic su Anno: tengo Brand+Talent, azzero Anno+Mese
          sel.year   = "";
          sel.month  = "";
        } else if (jump === stepMap.month) {
          // Clic su Mese: tengo tutto, azzero solo Mese
          sel.month  = "";
        }
      } else if (searchMode === 'roster') {
        // Un solo chip: Talent
        sel.talent = "";
      } else if (searchMode === 'estimate') {
        // Un solo chip: Talent
        sel.talent = "";
      }

      step = jump;     // torno allo step cliccato
      renderAll();     // ricalcolo wizard + risultati
    };
  }


  // Mostra / nascondi RESET + EXPORT GROUP
  const hasSelection = (searchMode === 'talent')
    ? (sel.talent || sel.year || sel.month || sel.brand || sel.campaign)
    : (searchMode === 'brand')
      ? (sel.brand || sel.campaign || sel.talent || sel.year || sel.month)
      : (searchMode === 'roster' || searchMode === 'estimate')
        ? (!!sel.talent)
        : false;

  const showReset = hasSelection && (searchMode !== 'roster');
  els.btnReset.style.display = showReset ? '' : 'none';
  els.btnReset.onclick = resetAllSelections;

  // FIX: Export visibile solo se il wizard √® finito
    const isFinished = (searchMode === 'talent')
      ? isTalentSelectionComplete()
      : (searchMode === 'brand')
        ? isBrandSelectionComplete()
        : (searchMode === 'roster' || searchMode === 'estimate')
          ? !!sel.talent
          : false;
  const canExport = isFinished && rowsFiltered().length > 0;
  
  // Update logic to show/hide the whole wrapper
    if(els.exportWrapper) {
      els.exportWrapper.style.display = (searchMode === 'roster' || searchMode === 'estimate') ? 'none' : (canExport ? 'inline-flex' : 'none');
    }

  if (els.filterShell && els.rosterDownloadBtn) {
    const rosterBar = (searchMode === 'roster');
    els.filterShell.classList.toggle('roster-download', rosterBar);
    els.rosterDownloadBtn.style.display = rosterBar ? 'flex' : 'none';
    if (rosterBar) {
      const isWall = sel.talent === '__ALL_TALENTS__';
      const label = isWall
        ? 'SCARICA IL ROSTER COMPLETO'
        : `SCARICA LA SCHEDA DI ${prettyLabel(sel.talent)}`;
      els.rosterDownloadBtn.textContent = label;
    }
  }

  setStateMessage('');
}


function renderResults(){
  // ROSTER MODE: gestione dedicata
  if (searchMode === 'roster'){
    // Wizard: un solo step -> finito quando c'√® il talent
    const finished = !!sel.talent && !editing;
    els.stepPanel.style.display = finished ? 'none' : '';

    // Nascondi dashboard standard
    els.mini.style.display = 'none'; els.mini.innerHTML = '';
    els.kpis.style.display = 'none'; els.kpis.innerHTML = '';
    els.tableWrap.style.display = 'none';
    if (els.exportWrapper) els.exportWrapper.style.display = 'none';

    // Render roster se finito
    if (finished){
      renderRoster();
    } else {
      const rosterEl = document.getElementById('roster');
      if (rosterEl){ rosterEl.style.display='none'; rosterEl.innerHTML=''; }
    }
    return;
  }

  // ESTIMATE MODE: gestione dedicata
  if (searchMode === 'estimate') {
    const finished = !!sel.talent && !editing;
    els.stepPanel.style.display = finished ? 'none' : '';

    // Nascondi dashboard standard e tabella
    els.tableWrap.style.display = 'none';
    els.tbody.innerHTML = '';
    if (els.exportWrapper) els.exportWrapper.style.display = 'none';

    // Nascondi roster quando non sei in modalit√† roster
    const rosterEl = document.getElementById('roster');
    if (rosterEl) { rosterEl.style.display = 'none'; rosterEl.innerHTML = ''; }

    if (!finished) {
      els.mini.style.display = 'none'; els.mini.innerHTML = '';
      els.kpis.style.display = 'none'; els.kpis.innerHTML = '';
      return;
    }

    const snapshot = buildEstimateSnapshot(sel.talent, 3);
    const estimateRows = snapshot.rows;
    const periodLabels = snapshot.periodLabels;

    if (!estimateRows.length) {
      els.mini.style.display = 'none';
      els.mini.innerHTML = '';
      els.kpis.style.display = '';
      els.kpis.innerHTML = `<div class="roster-empty">Nessun dato NO ADV disponibile negli ultimi 3 mesi.</div>`;
      return;
    }

    const typesSummary = computeContentTypesSummary(estimateRows);
    const periodDotsHtml = periodLabels.length
      ? periodLabels.map(m => `<span class="period-badge">${esc(m)}</span>`).join('')
      : `<span class="muted">N/A</span>`;
    const typePillsHtml = typesSummary.parts.length
      ? typesSummary.parts.map(p => `<span class="glass-pill ${p.bucket.toLowerCase()}">${esc(p.label)}</span>`).join('')
      : `<span class="muted">N/A</span>`;

    els.mini.style.display = 'grid';
    els.mini.innerHTML = `
      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-title">Periodo stimato</div>
        <div class="bento-content">${periodDotsHtml}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-title">Contenuti considerati</div>
        <div class="bento-content">${typePillsHtml}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-title">Filtro</div>
        <div class="bento-content">
          <span class="period-badge">NO ADV</span>
        </div>
      </div>`;

    // Stime divise per bucket social
    const buckets = {};
    for (const r of estimateRows) {
      const b = getBucket(r[COLS.type]);
      (buckets[b] ||= []).push(r);
    }

    const order = ["IGS", "REEL", "POST", "TIKTOK", "ALTRO"];
    const bucketKeys = Object.keys(buckets).sort((a, b) => (order.indexOf(a) - order.indexOf(b)) || a.localeCompare(b, undefined, { numeric: true }));

    els.kpis.style.display = '';
    els.kpis.innerHTML = bucketKeys.map(key => {
      const activeArr = buckets[key] || [];
      const n = activeArr.length;

      const viewsVal = avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.views);
      const vals = {
        reach: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.reach),
        link: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.linkClicks),
        tag: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.tagClicks),
        like: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.likes),
        commenti: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.comments),
        save: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.saves),
        share: avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.shares)
      };

      const periodCount = periodLabels.length || 0;
      const periodLabel = periodCount <= 0
        ? 'Periodo non disponibile'
        : (periodCount === 1 ? 'Ultimo 1 mese' : `Ultimi ${periodCount} mesi`);
      const subLabel = `${periodLabel} ¬∑ ${n} ${n === 1 ? 'contenuto' : 'contenuti'}`;
      const metricsList = (METRICS_BY_BUCKET[key] || METRICS_BY_BUCKET.ALTRO)
        .map(mk => `<li><span class="label">${METRIC_LABELS[mk]}</span><span class="val">${disp(vals[mk])}</span></li>`)
        .join('');
      const bucketClass = ["IGS", "TIKTOK", "REEL", "POST"].includes(key) ? key : "ALTRO";

      return `
      <div class="summary-card bucket-${bucketClass}">
         <div class="summary-card-bg bucket-${bucketClass}"></div>
         <div class="summary-card-content">
            <div class="title">
                <span>${esc(key)}</span>
                <span class="pill">Stima</span>
            </div>
            <div class="big">${disp(viewsVal)}</div>
            <div class="sub">${subLabel}</div>
            <ul>${metricsList}</ul>
         </div>
      </div>`;
    }).join('');

    return;
  }

  const rows = rowsFiltered();
  // ... existing code for wizard visibility ...
  const isFinished = (searchMode === 'talent')
    ? isTalentSelectionComplete()
    : (searchMode === 'brand')
      ? isBrandSelectionComplete()
      : !!sel.month;
  els.stepPanel.style.display = (editing || !isFinished) ? '' : 'none';
  
  // Nascondi roster quando non sei in modalit√† roster
  const rosterEl = document.getElementById('roster');
  if (rosterEl) { rosterEl.style.display = 'none'; rosterEl.innerHTML = ''; }
  
  const showDashboard = isFinished && rows.length > 0;

  if (showDashboard){
    // ... existing Bento summary rendering ...
    const periodMonths = getPeriodMonths(rows);
    const typesSummary = computeContentTypesSummary(rows);
    const rawMonths = uniq(rows.map(r => String(r[COLS.month]||''))).sort((a,b)=>monthKey(a)-monthKey(b));
    const showFullMonth = rawMonths.length <= 2;
    const periodDotsHtml = rawMonths.length ? rawMonths.map(m => {
            let label = monthName(m); 
            if (showFullMonth) {
                const clean = String(m||'').replace(/^\s*\d{1,2}\s*[-‚Äì]\s*/,'').trim();
                label = toTitleCase(clean);
            }
            return `<span class="period-badge">${esc(label)}</span>`;
        }).join('') : `<span class="muted">N/A</span>`;
    const typePillsHtml = typesSummary.parts.length ? typesSummary.parts.map(p => `<span class="glass-pill ${p.bucket.toLowerCase()}">${esc(p.label)}</span>`).join('') : `<span class="muted">N/A</span>`;

    els.mini.style.display = 'grid';
    els.mini.innerHTML = `
      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-title">Periodo dell'attivit√†</div>
        <div class="bento-content">${periodDotsHtml}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-title">Contenuti pubblicati</div>
        <div class="bento-content">${typePillsHtml}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-title">Pubblicazioni totali</div>
        <div class="bento-content total">
          <div class="kpi-hero">
            <div class="kpi-number">${typesSummary.totalPublications || 0}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>`;
  } else {
    els.mini.style.display = 'none';
    els.mini.innerHTML = '';
  }

  // --- KPI CARDS LOGIC WITH ADV FILTERS ---
  if (showDashboard) {
    els.kpis.style.display = '';
    
    // 1. Organize data into Buckets
    const buckets = {};
    for (const r of rows) { 
        const b = getBucket(r[COLS.type]); 
        (buckets[b] ||= []).push(r); 
    }

    const order = ["IGS","REEL","POST","TIKTOK","ALTRO"];
    const bucketKeys = Object.keys(buckets).sort((a,b)=> (order.indexOf(a) - order.indexOf(b)) || a.localeCompare(b, undefined, {numeric:true}));
    
    els.kpis.innerHTML = bucketKeys.map(key => {
      const originalArr = buckets[key]; 
      
      // Check if this bucket has any ADV content at all
      const hasAdvContent = originalArr.some(r => r.isAdv);
      
      // Filter logic based on user selection for this bucket
      let activeArr = originalArr;
      const filterMode = bucketFilters[key] || 'ALL'; // Default to ALL

      if (filterMode === 'ADV') {
          activeArr = originalArr.filter(r => r.isAdv);
      } else if (filterMode === 'NO_ADV') {
          activeArr = originalArr.filter(r => !r.isAdv);
      }

      // If activeArr is empty after filtering, we still show the card but with 0 values or handle it?
      // Design decision: Show card with N/A or 0.
      const n = activeArr.length;
      
      // Calculate Metrics
      const isSum = aggMode === "somma";
      const calc = (col) => isSum ? sumMetric(activeArr, col) : avgMetric(activeArr, col);
      
      const viewsVal = calc(COLS.views);
      const vals = { 
        reach: isSum ? null : avgMetric(activeArr, COLS.reach),
        link: calc(COLS.linkClicks), 
        tag: calc(COLS.tagClicks), 
        like: calc(COLS.likes), 
        commenti: calc(COLS.comments), 
        save: calc(COLS.saves), 
        share: calc(COLS.shares) 
      };
      
      const modeLabel = isSum ? "Somma" : "Media";
      const viewsText = n === 1 ? "Views" : (isSum ? "Views totali" : "Views medie");
      const subLabel  = viewsText + ` ¬∑ ${n} ${n===1?'contenuto':'contenuti'}`;
      const metricsList = (METRICS_BY_BUCKET[key] || METRICS_BY_BUCKET.ALTRO).map(mk => `<li><span class="label">${METRIC_LABELS[mk]}</span><span class="val">${disp(vals[mk])}</span></li>`).join('');
      const bucketClass = ["IGS","TIKTOK","REEL","POST"].includes(key) ? key : "ALTRO";

      // Render Title with Dropdown if needed
      let titleHtml = `<span>${esc(key)}</span>`;
      let dropdownHtml = '';
      
      // If bucket has ADV content available, render dropdown trigger
      if (hasAdvContent) {
          titleHtml = `
            <div class="bucket-title-wrapper has-dropdown" data-bucket="${escAttr(key)}">
                <span>${esc(key)}</span>
                <span class="bucket-arrow">‚ñº</span>
            </div>`;
            
          const activeClass = (val) => (filterMode === val ? 'active' : '');
          dropdownHtml = `
            <div class="bucket-dropdown" id="dropdown-${escAttr(key)}">
                <button class="bucket-opt ${activeClass('ALL')}" data-val="ALL">Tutti</button>
                <button class="bucket-opt ${activeClass('ADV')}" data-val="ADV">Solo ADV</button>
                <button class="bucket-opt ${activeClass('NO_ADV')}" data-val="NO_ADV">No ADV</button>
            </div>
          `;
      }

      // Hide pill when there's only one content (show only data without Media/Somma label)
      const showPill = n !== 1;
      const pillHtml = showPill ? `<span class="pill">${modeLabel}</span>` : '';

      // Structure: Outer Card > Background Layer (clipped) + Content Layer (overflow visible for menu)
      return `
      <div class="summary-card bucket-${bucketClass}">
         <div class="summary-card-bg bucket-${bucketClass}"></div>
         <div class="summary-card-content">
            <div class="title">
                ${titleHtml}
                ${pillHtml}
            </div>
            ${dropdownHtml}
            <div class="big">${disp(viewsVal)}</div>
            <div class="sub">${subLabel}</div>
            <ul>${metricsList}</ul>
         </div>
      </div>`;
    }).join('');

  } else {
    els.kpis.style.display = 'none';
  }

  // Table Logic (uses active filter too? No, usually table shows row filtered by global filters.
  // BUT: consistency suggests table should show what the cards show.
  // However, buckets are split. If I filter TikTok to ADV only, but Reels to ALL, the table becomes mixed.
  // Complex. Let's keep the table showing ALL filtered by global selection (Talent/Month) to be safe/simple, 
  // OR apply filter if a specific bucket filter is active?
  // User request: "ognuno di questi farlo diventare un men√π a tendina" -> implies per-card filtering.
  // The table is a global list. Let's leave the table showing ALL for now to avoid confusion, 
  // or (Advanced) filter the table rows based on the composite filter state.
  // Decision: Filter table rows to match visual cards.
  
  if (showDashboard) {
    els.tableWrap.style.display = '';
    
    // Apply Bucket Filters to rows for Table display
    let tableRows = rows;
    
    // If any bucket filter is active (!= ALL), we must filter rows that belong to that bucket
    const activeBucketKeys = Object.keys(bucketFilters);
    if (activeBucketKeys.length > 0) {
        tableRows = rows.filter(r => {
            const b = getBucket(r[COLS.type]);
            const filter = bucketFilters[b] || 'ALL';
            if (filter === 'ALL') return true;
            if (filter === 'ADV') return r.isAdv;
            if (filter === 'NO_ADV') return !r.isAdv;
            return true;
        });
    }

    const sorted = [...tableRows].sort((a,b) => (monthKey(a[COLS.month]) - monthKey(b[COLS.month])) || norm(a[COLS.brand]).localeCompare(norm(b[COLS.brand])) || norm(a[COLS.type]).localeCompare(norm(b[COLS.type]), undefined, {numeric:true}));
    
    els.tbody.innerHTML = sorted.map(r=>{
      const link = r[COLS.link] || '';
      const linkAttr = link ? ` data-link="${escAttr(link)}"` : '';
      return `<tr${linkAttr}><td>${esc(formatBrandForTable(r[COLS.brand]))}</td><td>${esc(monthName(r[COLS.month]))}</td><td>${esc(r[COLS.type])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.views])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.reach])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.linkClicks])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.tagClicks])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.likes])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.comments])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.saves])}</td><td>${disp(r[COLS.shares])}</td></tr>`;
    }).join('');
  } else {
    els.tableWrap.style.display = 'none';
    els.tbody.innerHTML = '';
  }
}

function updateRosterWallState(){
  const isWall = searchMode === 'roster' && sel.talent === '__ALL_TALENTS__';
  document.body.classList.toggle('roster-wall-active', isWall);
}

function renderAll(){
  updateRosterWallState();
  renderWizard();
  renderResults();
}

function renderAllTalentsRoster() {
  const rosterEl = document.getElementById('roster');
  if (!rosterEl) return;

  const rowsHtml = ROSTER_WALL_ROWS.map((row) => {
    const tiles = row.map((talentName) => {
      const src = rosterPhotoSrc(talentName);
      return `<button class="roster-tile" type="button" data-roster-talent="${escAttr(talentName)}" aria-label="${escAttr(talentName)}"><img src="${escAttr(src)}" alt="${escAttr(talentName)}" loading="lazy"></button>`;
    }).join('');
    return `<div class="roster-wall-row" style="--roster-cols:${row.length};">${tiles}</div>`;
  }).join('');

  rosterEl.innerHTML = `<div class="roster-wall">${rowsHtml}</div>`;
  rosterEl.style.display = 'block';
}

function renderRoster(){
  const rosterEl = document.getElementById('roster');
  if (!rosterEl) return;
  const talentName = sel.talent || '';
  const isWall = talentName === '__ALL_TALENTS__';
  rosterEl.classList.toggle('roster-wall-view', isWall);
  
  // Se √® selezionato "Tutti i talent", usa la funzione dedicata
  if (isWall) {
    renderAllTalentsRoster();
    return;
  }
  
  console.log('[ROSTER] Cerco talent:', talentName);
  console.log('[ROSTER] FOLLOWERS totali:', FOLLOWERS.length);
  
  const rows = getRosterRowsForTalent(talentName);
  console.log('[ROSTER] Righe trovate per nome:', rows.length);
  
  if (rows.length > 0) {
    console.log('[ROSTER] Esempio prima riga:', rows[0]);
  }

  const byPlat = latestByPlatform(rows);
  const growthSeries = buildRosterPlatformSeries(rows);
  console.log('[ROSTER] Piattaforme estratte:', byPlat);

  // Mappa piattaforme supportate
  const talentId = safeSvgId(talentName);
  const PLATS = [
    { key:['INSTAGRAM','IG'], platform:'INSTAGRAM', id:'ig', label:'Followers', icon:`<svg class="platform-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><linearGradient
